fields.description: Base64-encoded encrypted data that produces a full resource respresented as JSON. The data has been encrypted with the provided dataKey using an AES/CBC/PKCS5PADDING cipher suite.
fields.name: Data

fields.description: Base64-encoded symmetric key generated by Microsoft Graph to encrypt the data value and to generate the data signature. This key is encrypted with the certificate public key that was provided during the subscription. It must be decrypted with the certificate private key before it can be used to decrypt the data or verify the signature. This key has been encrypted with the following cipher suite: RSA/ECB/OAEPWithSHA1AndMGF1Padding.
fields.name: DataKey

fields.description: Base64-encoded HMAC-SHA256 hash of the data for validation purposes.
fields.name: DataSignature

fields.description: ID of the certificate used to encrypt the dataKey.
fields.name: EncryptionCertificateId

fields.description: Hexadecimal representation of the thumbprint of the certificate used to encrypt the dataKey.
fields.name: EncryptionCertificateThumbprint

fields.description: The OData ID of this entity
fields.name: ODataId

fields.description: The OData Type of this entity
fields.name: ODataType
